OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry morning with
OL,6,Fsunny spells and the odd light shower.
OL,7,FBecoming cloudier with showers
OL,8,Fdeveloping more widely over Argyll and
OL,9,FTrossachs in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FBright spells and scattered
OL,12,Fshowers in the evening. Showers
OL,13,Fbecoming confined to the Argyll coast
OL,14,Fovernight with long clear spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA bright and mostly sunny
OL,18,Fstart. Cloud increasing through the
OL,19,Fmorning with some light showers
OL,20,Ffeeding down from the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
